embeds.title: That player doesn't have premium!
embeds.description: In order to view stats for 2025, a [premium subscription](https://statalytics.net/store) is required!

fields.name: How does it work?
fields.value:
`-` You can view any player's stats for 2025 if you have a premium subscription.
 `-` You can view a player's stats for 2025 if they have a premium subscription.
